HEADWORD: outpouring
<hw>out"pour`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An unrestrained expression (of
emotion, feeling); <as>as, an <ex>outpouring</ex> of grief over the
death of Princess Diana</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
